{"type": "article", "id": 24319, "title": "北欧家居品牌 iittala 在台北开新店，是香港人设计的", "description": "在芬兰， iittala 被称为“国民品牌”，他们的设计也一直在被其他品牌仿效。", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11845, "name": "台北"}, {"id": 22293, "name": "家居品牌"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}, {"id": 23349, "name": "Iittala"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151740gUD08oJ4GpLtBM1n.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">家居领域的北欧风继续在东方国家强劲地刮。最近，芬兰著名的<a href=\"https://www.iittala.com/home\">家居品牌 iittala </a>便看中了台湾市场，<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/design/michael-young-designs-taipei-iittala-showroom#151323\">在台北开设了一家旗舰店</a>，这是他们在亚洲为数不多的店铺之一。这家店铺是香港建筑师 Michael Young 设计的，在 85 平米大的空间里，Michael Young 使用了不少木材和铝架。架子上摆满了 iittala 的餐具、炊具和家居纺织品，这也是  iittala 旗下的三大产品线。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021517282ejoL3iknP5t8ARI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">iittala 台北新店，占地面积 85 平米，乍看之下稍有些乱</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151728vfysuSp0tAzcgIXJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">但店铺风格很亲民    </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021517293R9UI4ALN0rmOeDn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">iittala 的招牌产品就是玻璃杯</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151730jil6foxZMWeqdKRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Iittala 是每个芬兰家庭都熟悉的品牌，从花器到餐具，从瓷器到玻璃，它占据了芬兰家庭的许多角落。</p>\n<p>其实 iittala 是芬兰首都赫尔辛基的一个小镇名称，这个小镇一直以玻璃制品闻名。玻璃和陶瓷一向是芬兰设计的强项，他们作品灵感往往来自于大自然的启示。130 多年前 iittala 成立了，一百多年来，它成长为了北欧玻璃器皿现代设计的代表。它的玻璃制品有着简洁的线条、易于搭配的设计，杯子还使用了独有的 I-crystal 无铅水晶玻璃，这种玻璃有着水晶般的透光度和折射度，被许多人所喜爱。</p>\n<p>现代建筑师 Alvar Aalto 1936 年的湖泊系列、设计师 Tapio Wirkkala 1968 年设计的极冻系列都传承至今。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151730q7vfUGw9ZlJ08esL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> iittala 花纹系列产品 </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215173119MF3slv4kLjJNZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81120332\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Enssence 系列的杯子</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151731KEpfxzryNb6nWFJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">iittala 和三宅一生合作推出的家居系列产品   </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151732wx3VXT8U5OBQpzZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151732diTLURrqjy36PgX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151733F7AUd8CngXVJHPfE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">与三宅一生的合作款玻璃杯</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151734me3DagGBPW69LCb0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21246459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Aalto 湖泊系列的花瓶</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151734OUqupTD6xv0XGz1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10921986\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">花瓶虽然很美，但价格高得有些惊人，京东上的售价是 3300 元人民币</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151736aVSwO3KJdjqk9xNY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Tapio Wirkkala 设计的极冻系列</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151736t6LP24k35sXSuTdh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这也是 Tapio Wirkkala 设计的作品</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151737YazlqrOU6PkmdH7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Tapio Wirkkala 本尊</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">以下是 iittala 设计的简约演化史：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021517378GP4e1cAtybmWZin.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151738VJkGdUgDtj6TyZKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42063492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151738pjwRmESZFVicbKUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57283951\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151739YTDVnbu0yoq15KUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>目前 iittala 在芬兰国内有 6 家实体店，在全球范围内共有 40 余家店铺。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/design/michael-young-designs-taipei-iittala-showroom#151323\">wallpaper</a></p>\n\n"}